PA4    MPU9_CS CS
PC13  ICM42_CS CS
PE10  BMIA_CS CS
PE12  BMIG_CS CS
PD10 EXT_CS2   CS
PD11 EXT_CS1   CS

PB5 FRAM_CS CS
PB7 SDCARD_CS CS

